'''José Guillermo Herrera Mendoza''' (born 16 June 1960) is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] politician affiliated with the [[Convergence (Mexico)|Convergence]]. As of 2014 he served as Senator of the [[LIX Legislature of the Mexican Congress]] representing [[Veracruz]] as replacement of [[Armando Méndez de la Luz]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Perfil del legislador|url=http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Librerias/pp_PerfilLegislador.php?SID=&Referencia=1169704|publisher=Legislative Information System|accessdate=25 April 2014}}</ref>

